                        AssetConfig.sendMail, // Use a constant from AssetConfig
                        height: 250,
                        width: 250,
                      ),

                      // Verification text
                      Text(
                        'We Sent you an Email\nto reset your password',
                        style: AppColor.headingMedium.copyWith(
                          color: AppColor.inputTextColor,
